                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.414/10–2545: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        United States Political Adviser for Germany</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Murphy</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-10-31T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 31, 1945—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>774. Urtel 838, Oct 25. Proposed transfer of German FonOff documents to Brit zone
                    should not be effected pending discussion of policy here at high level. Please
                    inform U.S. military authorities accordingly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
